item.title: CVE-2021-44170|2024-08-04T04:17:24.928Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortiproxy%2C%20fortios
item.description: A stack-based buffer overflow vulnerability [CWE-121] in the command line interpreter of FortiOS before 7.0.4 and FortiProxy before 2.0.8 may allow an authenticated attacker to execute unauthorized code or commands via specially crafted command line arguments.
